        <p class="lead font-serif text-xl">How you begin your day sets the tone for everything that follows. A thoughtfully designed morning routine doesn't just prepare you for the day ahead—it transforms those first waking hours into a luxurious ritual that nourishes your body, mind, and spirit. In this article, we explore the elements of a perfect morning routine that balances wellness, productivity, and pleasure.</p>
        
